they are available for viewing

00:01:02.620 --> 00:01:04.890
to Internet patrons
throughout the world.

00:01:04.890 --> 00:01:07.950
So, if you haven't already done
so, now would be an excellent time

00:01:07.950 --> 00:01:12.110
to turn off any electronic
devices you have with you.

00:01:12.110 --> 00:01:15.220
