involved in setting traditions

00:01:50.350 --> 00:01:55.890
and practices surrounding food,
food preparation and preservation

00:01:55.890 --> 00:01:59.640
and the use of food in
rituals and celebration.

00:01:59.640 --> 00:02:03.010
The American Folklife Center
archive contains an enormous amount

00:02:03.010 --> 00:02:08.880
of materials about food and
food-related traditions,

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:13.790
