00:04:02.270 --> 00:04:05.250
I'm interested in the technologies
involved, in the artifacts

00:04:05.250 --> 00:04:08.540 position:56%
and processes that turn perishable
matter into stuff that can be stored

00:04:08.540 --> 00:04:11.780
and exchanged according
to human desires,

00:04:11.780 --> 00:04:14.460
but I want to also know how
technology -- excuse me --

00:04:14.460 --> 00:04:17.810
I want to know how technologies
themselves in the societies

00:04:17.810 --> 00:04:21.050
