dehydration practices that continue

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:39.030
because they make sense in terms
of local tastes, social structures,

00:06:39.030 --> 00:06:42.260
built environments and
values, such as reluctance

00:06:42.260 --> 00:06:45.740
