00:07:50.110 --> 00:07:54.150
Here's one last photo
from the AFC collections.

00:07:54.150 --> 00:07:56.010 position:56%
This is from the Coal River Project.

00:07:56.010 --> 00:07:59.050
Here is an example of "leather
britches beans" strung on thread

00:07:59.050 --> 00:08:01.110
