help her win some social status.

00:21:02.020 --> 00:21:04.440
Another sort of ideograph
or narrative

00:21:04.440 --> 00:21:06.520
that indexes this idea
of abundance, right?

00:21:06.520 --> 00:21:08.970
So here we're back
