00:30:43.310 --> 00:30:44.730
in the bottling of
vegetables and meat.

00:30:44.730 --> 00:30:47.870
U- to-date canning guidelines
are important and I encourage you

00:30:47.870 --> 00:30:50.670
to consult the National Center
for Home Food Preservation

00:30:50.670 --> 00:30:54.020
