violence to localized knowledge,

00:31:31.220 --> 00:31:33.740
which is learned through lifetimes
of observation and practice

00:31:33.740 --> 00:31:37.590
and developed within circumscribed
intertwined ecosystems.

00:31:37.590 --> 00:31:40.630
In the case of home canning, I'm
going to focus on two examples

00:31:40.630 --> 00:31:43.400
